Package ohos.agp.window.service

Class DisplayNotch

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.window.service.DisplayNotch

  • public class DisplayNotch
extends Object
    Represents a display notch, which cannot be used for displaying content.

    You can use the methods in this class to obtain the notch size and safe padding on a device.

    Since:
    5
